{"title":"IPH 246 - You servants of God","verses":[{"lines":["You servants of God, your"," master proclaim,"," and publish abroad His"," wonderful name;","\fthe name all – victorious of"," Jesus extol,","His kingdom is glorious, and"," rules over all"]},{"lines":["\f God rules in the height,"," almighty to save –","though hid from our sight,"," His presence we have;","\fthe great congregation His"," triumph shall sing,","ascribing salvation to Jesus"," our King."]},{"lines":["\f‘Salvation to God who sits"," on the throne!”"," Let all cry aloud, and"," honour the Son;","\f the praises of Jesus the"," angels proclaim,","fall down on their faces and"," worship the Lamb"]},{"lines":["\fThen let us all adore and"," give Him His right"," all glory and power, all"," wisdom and might,","\f all honour and blessing –"," with angels above –"," and thanks never ceasing,"," and infinite love."]}],"chorus":"","CCLI":"Charles Wesley, 1707-1788 CCLI 128675\r"}